title: Registered Cellular Antenna Structure Locations, Florida, 2008
name: Registered Cellular Antenna Structure Locations, Florida, 2008
description:
Abstract: This dataset contains FCC registered cellular antenna structure locations.
Purpose: This dataset represents FCC registered cellular antenna structures. This mobile cellular service list mobile radiotelephone service in which common carriers are authorized to offer and provide a mobile telecommunications service for hire to the general public using cellular systems.
